#~ msgid ""
#~ "Founder and chief visionary, Tony is the driving force behind the "
#~ "company. He loves to keep his hands full by participating in the "
#~ "development of the magazine and does not hesitate to carry out field "
#~ "surveys."
#~ msgstr ""
